Use the standard library
This is how to flip_case of string:
  Remember that result is ""
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this string's length times:
    Remember that ch is item i in string
    When ch is in "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz", then:
      Remember that result is "{result}{tostring of diff of toint of ch and 32}"
    But, if not:
      When ch is in "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ", then:
        Remember that result is "{result}{tostring of sum of toint of ch and 32}"
      But, if not:
        Remember that result is "{result}{ch}"
      End when
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know